parameters:
Innkeeper: I've handed over everything that seems useful in
this emergency situation.

Innkeeper: Please, win for us. If things continue like this,
even if we survive, the inn will go under.

It was the right decision to follow Prince Lex, who would
even kill civilians for his own sake, said the soldier loyal
to the prince.

Prince's soldier: I took an arrow to the knee... It's
frustrating that I can't fight for Lord Rex.

Inn Receptionist: We are lending the second floor to the
injured soldiers, so you cannot use the inn. Instead, please
take this.

Inn Receptionist: We are lending the second floor to the
injured soldiers.

Elderly Worker: They were making a fuss about a dragon
appearing, completely drunk and spouting nonsense.

Innkeeper: Is this place safe?! I absolutely don't want to
die without getting married!

Prince's Army Soldier: Damn those members of the Dark
Division... My arm is paralyzed and I can't fight... Damn
it!

I would be happy if Simos, the man who was saved by someone
from the guild, could thank him.

Queen's Army Soldier: Caron, who has tarnished the history
of the empire and the royal family, has become an enemy of
all imperial citizens. I can't forgive her either.
Clea: Piste-san, why are you here!?

Receptionist Piste: It's no surprise that I'm the only one
in the safe zone... Right now, this place feels like an
impromptu field hospital.

Receptionist Piste: I'm also providing medical treatment, so
if you want to recover, leave it to me!

Receptionist Piste: ...If you die, I won't be able to heal
you, so please make sure not to push yourself too hard,
okay?

Receptionist Piste: Oh right, this... It's from Shimosu-
san, for Clea-chan and the others.

Receptionist Piste: As I said before, you know? I may not
look like a bad person, sniffs, I'm sorry...

Clea: Thank you very much, Piste-san. I will have Shimosu-
san come up to the rooftop with us.
Receptionist Piste: Are you going to recover here?

Receptionist Piste: You mustn't push yourself too hard,
okay!
Receptionist Piste: Make sure to take a good rest, okay!

Prince's soldier: I'm sorry, please step aside! We have
injured people, we need to carry them up to the second
floor!

Cleric Sophia: I'll help too. I'm a cleric, so there must be
something I can do.

Prince's soldier: That's appreciated! With two clerics, we
can feel relieved!
Prince's soldier: Come with us up to the second floor!
